      <title>TGI Friday’s 是最新一家破产的休闲餐饮连锁店</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/tgi-friday-s-becomes-latest-casual-dining-chain-to-go-bankrupt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[休闲餐饮连锁店 TGI Friday’s Inc. 申请破产保护，原因是难以扭转业务困境，受到越来越注重成本的消费者的压力，这些消费者在外出就餐时要么变得更加挑剔，要么更喜欢提供快餐的竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/tgi-friday-s-becomes-latest-casual-dining-chain-to-go-bankrupt</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 07:24:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
